ZH: 制造者负责组装生产线上的机器。
EN: The manufacturer is responsible for assembling the machines on the production line.

ZH: 制造者需要确保产品符合质量标准。
EN: The manufacturer needs to ensure that the products meet quality standards.

ZH: 制造者必须遵守相关法规和标准。
EN: The manufacturer must comply with relevant regulations and standards.

ZH: 制造者在制定生产计划时需要考虑市场需求。
EN: The manufacturer needs to consider market demand when planning production.

ZH: 制造者还要负责产品的包装和运输。
EN: The manufacturer is also responsible for packaging and transportation of the products.

ZH: 制造者应该不断提高生产效率。
EN: The manufacturer should continuously improve production efficiency.

ZH: 制造者在生产过程中应该关注产品质量。
EN: The manufacturer should pay attention to product quality during the production process.

ZH: 制造者必须确保原材料的供应稳定。
EN: The manufacturer must ensure the stable supply of raw materials.

ZH: 制造者应该建立良好的合作关系。
EN: The manufacturer should establish good cooperative relationships.

ZH: 制造者需要密切关注市场变化。
EN: The manufacturer needs to closely monitor market changes.

ZH: 制造者要保证产品符合消费者需求。
EN: The manufacturer must ensure that the products meet consumer demand.

ZH: 制造者必须保护知识产权。
EN: The manufacturer must protect intellectual property rights.

ZH: 制造者应该投资研发新技术。
EN: The manufacturer should invest in researching and developing new technologies.

ZH: 制造者需要拥有高素质的员工。
EN: The manufacturer needs to have high-quality employees.

ZH: 制造者应该确保工作场所安全。
EN: The manufacturer should ensure workplace safety.

ZH: 制造者必须遵循环保法规。
EN: The manufacturer must comply with environmental regulations.

ZH: 制造者需要处理客户投诉。
EN: The manufacturer needs to handle customer complaints.

ZH: 制造者应该与供应商建立互惠关系。
EN: The manufacturer should establish mutually beneficial relationships with suppliers.

ZH: 制造者要做好产品售后服务。
EN: The manufacturer needs to provide good after-sales service.

ZH: 制造者对产品的质量负有最终责任。
EN: The manufacturer has the ultimate responsibility for the quality of the product.
